<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>RotMG Art Maker - Account Verification</title>
    <style>
        body {
            line-height: 1;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        h1 {
            text-align: center;
        }

        p {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .verification-code {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .code-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .note {
            font-style: italic;
            color: #888;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>RotMG Art Maker - Account Verification</h1>
        <p>Dear [[[USERNAME]]],</p>
        <p>Thank you for registering an account with RotMG Art Maker. To complete the registration process and verify your account, please use the following verification link:</p>
        <div class="code-container">
            <a class="verification-code" href="[[[LINK]]]" target="_blank">Verify my account</a>
        </div>
        <p class="note">Note: This verification link is valid for [[[DURATION]]]. If you did not request this verification or if you believe this email was sent in error, please disregard it.</p>
        <p>If you have any questions or need further assistance, please contact us at admin@rotmgartmaker.com.</p>
        <p>Thank you,<br>RotMG Art Maker Team</p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>